data.name: label6.Text
data.value: CT150 is powered by a 4-stroke, air-cooled, single-cylinder engine that is guaranteed to provide you the power and acceleration that you need! The new CT150 now comes with a new fuel tank with a large capacity of 10.5 liters. It also comes with a TC ready frame and new instrument panel with mobile charger for the convenience of the everyday Filipino rider.
